00010172 - **臨床藥理學 Clinical pharmacology , Fall  2010











Clinical pharmacology
臨床藥理學
Instructor:
張念中
Nen-Chung Chang
School of Medicine
            Taipei Medical University
Course Structure: 2 hour per a week
  TMU Podcast 播客





Image courtesy of eduCommons (275px x 275px)
Course Description
To introduce the mechanisms of medications in the clinical use and to demonstrate the purpose (indications) and side effects and expectance of these medications
臨床藥理學內容乃是註重於臨床藥物之機轉,使用目的,副作用以及預期效果的教學,並以針對各類疾病的藥物使用,俾讓高年級醫學生至醫院實習時能更易進入狀況,來進行此一教學課程

開課系所:醫學系
開課年級:醫5
學分:1






